#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an5.308"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:0.2"
msgid "29. Rāgapeyyāla "
msgstr "29. Abbreviated Texts Beginning With Greed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:0.3"
msgid "308–1152 "
msgstr "308–1152 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:1.1"
msgid "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, pariññāya … parikkhayāya … pahānāya … khayāya … vayāya … virāgāya … nirodhāya … cāgāya … paṭinissaggāya pañca dhammā bhāvetabbā. "
msgstr "“For the complete understanding … finishing … giving up … ending … vanishing … fading away … cessation … giving away … letting go of greed, five things should be developed.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:1.2"
msgid "Dosassa … mohassa … kodhassa … upanāhassa … makkhassa … paḷāsassa … issāya … macchariyassa … māyāya … sāṭheyyassa … thambhassa … sārambhassa … mānassa … atimānassa … madassa … pamādassa abhiññāya … pariññāya … parikkhayāya … pahānāya … khayāya … vayāya … virāgāya … nirodhāya … cāgāya … paṭinissaggāya pañca dhammā bhāvetabbā. (6–849.) "
msgstr "“Of hate … delusion … anger … hostility … offensiveness … contempt … jealousy … stinginess … deceit … deviousness … obstinacy … aggression … conceit … arrogance … vanity … negligence … for insight … complete understanding … finishing … giving up … ending … vanishing … fading away … cessation … giving away … letting go … five things should be developed. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:2.1"
msgid "Katame pañca? "
msgstr "What five? "

msgctxt "an5.308-1152:2.2"
msgid "Saddhābalaṃ, vīriyabalaṃ, satibalaṃ, samādhibalaṃ, paññābalaṃ—"
msgstr "The powers of faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom. "

msgctxt "an5.308-1152:2.3"
msgid "pamādassa, bhikkhave, paṭinissaggāya ime pañca dhammā bhāvetabbā”ti. (850) "
msgstr "For the letting go of negligence, these five things should be developed.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:2.4"
msgid "Rāgapeyyālaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:3.1"
msgid "Abhiññāya pariññāya parikkhayāya, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:3.2"
msgid "Pahānāya khayāya vayena ca; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:3.3"
msgid "Virāganirodhā cāgañca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:3.4"
msgid "Paṭinissaggo ime dasāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:3.5"
msgid "Pañcakanipāto niṭṭhito. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="vagguddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.1"
msgid "Sekhabalaṃ balañceva, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.2"
msgid "Pañcaṅgikañca sumanaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.3"
msgid "Muṇḍanīvaraṇañca saññañca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.4"
msgid "Yodhājīvañca aṭṭhamaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.5"
msgid "Theraṃ kakudhaphāsuñca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.6"
msgid "Andhakavindadvādasaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.7"
msgid "Gilānarājatikaṇḍaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.8"
msgid "Saddhammāghātupāsakaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.9"
msgid "Araññabrāhmaṇañceva, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.10"
msgid "Kimilakkosakaṃ tathā; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.11"
msgid "Dīghācārāvāsikañca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.12"
msgid "Duccaritūpasampadanti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endbook">
msgctxt "an5.308-1152:4.13"
msgid "Pañcakanipātapāḷi niṭṭhitā. "
msgstr "The Book of the Fives is finished."

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
